pre-requisites:
   - lttoolbox 3.1 or above
   - apertium 3.1 or above
   - xsltproc

Compile:     
   $ sh compile.sh
--------

To get analysis:
----------------
  $lt-proc -c -a hi.morf.bin

Or use following command to run the input from file:
  $sh run_morph-analyser.sh <INPUT_FILE>
  Ex. 
    $sh run_morph-analyser.sh inp.txt

To get generation
-----------------
  $lt-proc -c -g hi.gen.bin
  
Or use following command to run the input from file:
  $sh run_morph-generator.sh <INPUT_FILE>
  Ex. 
    $sh run_morph-generator.sh inp-2
